race.comment: THE QUIET IMMORTAL (7) is a three start maiden who looks well placed here. Yet to run a bad race and looks ideally suited by the extra ground. Will box seat from the low draw and should go close. MISS NAVRATILOVA (14) has filled a minor placing at both runs to date, the latest when beaten 1.75 lengths into second over 1203m at Kyneton. Has upside and expected to go well. CANBECOSTLY (1) settled back and never came on when resuming over 1200m at Moe. Fitter and blinkers come off. Worth another chance. I SEE YOU BABY (10) wasn't far away last start over 1514m at Yarra Valley, beaten 2.25 lengths into fifth. Capable of featuring prominently. MORAL TURPITUDE (4) is overdue for a win and gets chance.
